      <title>Nintendo的股票估值激增后，Switch 2的赌注高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/stakes-high-for-switch-2-after-nintendo-s-stock-valuation-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nintendo Co.的股票已经飙升为一系列记录，以期预期其Switch 2游戏机，从而使该小工具的细节揭示了潜在的分水岭。]]></description>
